                <mxCell id="11" value="&lt;div style=&quot;font-family:monospace;font-size:10px;line-height:1.7;padding:4px;color:#1a1a1a;&quot;&gt; &lt;b&gt;credit-risk-dashboard/&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Vite · React&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;b&gt;── Calls ──────────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; POST /score/{segment}&lt;br/&gt; GET  /score-all/{segment}&lt;br/&gt; POST /score-customer/{segment}&lt;br/&gt; POST /cache/refresh&lt;br/&gt; GET  /health&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;b&gt;── Renders ────────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; Paginated risk table&lt;br/&gt; Customer drilldown&lt;br/&gt; Portfolio summary&lt;br/&gt; &lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;" parent="10" vertex="1">
