                <mxCell id="20" value="API GATEWAY  ·  api/scoring_api.py" style="swimlane;startSize=42;fillColor=#D5E8D4;strokeColor=#82B366;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#1a1a1a;swimlaneLine=1;rounded=4;arcSize=2;align=center;" parent="1" tooltip="FastAPI app · uvicorn api/scoring_api.py  STARTUP: lifespan() -&gt; _startup_checks() -&gt; load_production_artifacts() pre-warms XGBoost  BULK PATH (/score-all): score_all() -&gt; cache.get_scored_page() -&gt; cursor-paginated rows MANUAL PATH (/score): score() -&gt; build_risk_main_manual_request_frame() -&gt; score_production_frame() CUSTOMER PATH (/score-customer): live OR pinned snapshot via snapshotId  AUTH: require_api_key Depends() on score, score-customer, cache/refresh routes. RESPONSE: response_from_raw(raw_df, scored_df) -&gt; _shape_response_frame() -&gt; JSON" vertex="1">
