                <mxCell id="21" value="&lt;div style=&quot;font-family:monospace;font-size:10px;line-height:1.7;padding:4px;color:#1a1a1a;&quot;&gt; &lt;b&gt;── Routes ─────────────────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; score()               :144&lt;br/&gt; score_all()           :171&lt;br/&gt; score_customer()      :215&lt;br/&gt; refresh_cache()       :256&lt;br/&gt; health()              :274&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;b&gt;── Scoring Helpers ────────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; build_scored_frame()  :112&lt;br/&gt; build_scored_dataset() :136&lt;br/&gt; _prepare_history_frame() :102&lt;br/&gt; _enrich_with_customer_history() :107&lt;br/&gt; _resolve_threshold_override() :41&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;b&gt;── Startup ─────────────────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; lifespan()            :81&lt;br/&gt; _startup_checks()     :61&lt;br/&gt; _check_mongo_live()   :71&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;b&gt;── Auth / Models ───────────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; require_api_key   auth.py&lt;br/&gt; ApiSettings       settings.py&lt;br/&gt; ScoreRequest      models.py&lt;br/&gt; CustomerScoreRequest  models.py&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;b&gt;── Response Shaping ────────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; response_from_raw()   :332&lt;br/&gt; _shape_response_frame() :149&lt;br/&gt; _build_scored_summary() :167&lt;br/&gt; _build_customer_summary_payload() :245&lt;br/&gt; _aggregate_customer_top_features() :197&lt;br/&gt; _normalize_response_records() :39&lt;br/&gt; _filter_customer_rows() :44&lt;br/&gt; _derive_contract_fields() :95&lt;br/&gt; _normalize_top_features() :51&lt;br/&gt; display_feature_name()  risk_map.py:292&lt;br/&gt; &lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;" parent="20" vertex="1">
