                <mxCell id="30" value="CACHE ENGINE  ·  api/cache.py" style="swimlane;startSize=42;fillColor=#F8CECC;strokeColor=#AE4132;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#1a1a1a;swimlaneLine=1;rounded=4;arcSize=2;align=center;" parent="1" tooltip="Central caching hub — ApiCache class · api/cache.py  load_full_dataset(): calls pipeline -&gt; full Risk.Main df _build_scored_snapshot(): runs score_production_frame() on full_df -&gt; list[dict] in memory get_scored_page(): decodes cursor, slices positions, encodes next cursor (base64 JSON)  _worker() background thread: periodic refresh -&gt; load_full_dataset() + _build_scored_snapshot() _prune_previous_snapshot_locked(): TTL-expires old snapshots  DataFrames held: full_df (all Risk.Main rows), snapshot_records (list of scored dicts)" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="612" y="30" width="280" height="760" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="31" value="&lt;div style=&quot;font-family:monospace;font-size:10px;line-height:1.7;padding:4px;color:#1a1a1a;&quot;&gt; &lt;b&gt;── Dataset ─────────────────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; load_full_dataset()   :132&lt;br/&gt; _prepare_snapshot_frame() :91&lt;br/&gt; enrich_with_customer_history() :195&lt;br/&gt; fetch_customer_aggregates() :170&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;b&gt;── Snapshot ────────────────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; _build_scored_snapshot() :221&lt;br/&gt; load_scored_snapshot() :317&lt;br/&gt; _resolve_scored_snapshot() :356&lt;br/&gt; _positions_for_segment() :370&lt;br/&gt; get_scored_page()     :376&lt;br/&gt; get_snapshot_customer_frame() :453&lt;br/&gt; _prune_previous_snapshot_locked() :309&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;b&gt;── Cursor ──────────────────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; _encode_cursor()      :202&lt;br/&gt; _decode_cursor()      :206&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;b&gt;── Thread / Config ─────────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; _resolve_threshold()  :216&lt;br/&gt; _model_key()          :87&lt;br/&gt; _worker() [bg thread] :538&lt;br/&gt; refresh()             :475&lt;br/&gt; start() / stop()      :561 / 578&lt;br/&gt; snapshot()            :489&lt;br/&gt; &lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;" parent="30" vertex="1">
