                <mxCell id="40" value="DATA PIPELINE  ·  pipeline/" style="swimlane;startSize=42;fillColor=#E1D5E7;strokeColor=#9673A6;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#1a1a1a;swimlaneLine=1;rounded=4;arcSize=2;align=center;" parent="1" tooltip="DATA PIPELINE — pipeline/  4A: fetch_risk_main_frame() -&gt; projected MongoDB find() via get_database()     canonicalize_risk_main_frame(): flattens nested docs -&gt; flat pd.DataFrame     Internally calls: parse_main_date(), parse_payment_value()  4B: build_risk_main_scoring_frame(canonical_df):     chains 4A -&gt; features/engineering.py -&gt; customer_aggregates -&gt; point_in_time     -&gt; select_model_features() -&gt; feature_matrix_df  4D: score_mongo_frame() = full orchestrator: fetch-&gt;canonicalize-&gt;build-&gt;score  DataFrame emitted: raw_canonical_df (flat, all Risk.Main fields, dates parsed)" vertex="1">
