                <mxCell id="41" value="&lt;div style=&quot;font-family:monospace;font-size:10px;line-height:1.7;padding:4px;color:#1a1a1a;&quot;&gt; &lt;b&gt;── 4A · Fetch &amp;amp; Canonicalize ────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;i&gt;risk_canonical.py&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br/&gt; fetch_risk_main_frame()   :97&lt;br/&gt; canonicalize_risk_main_frame() :137&lt;br/&gt; load_canonical_risk_main_dataset() :235&lt;br/&gt; inspect_risk_main_indexes() :106&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;b&gt;── 4B · Scoring Frame ──────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;i&gt;risk_main.py&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br/&gt; fetch_production_risk_main_dataset() :19&lt;br/&gt; build_risk_main_scoring_frame() :35&lt;br/&gt; build_risk_main_customer_aggregates() :69&lt;br/&gt; build_risk_main_manual_request_frame() :117&lt;br/&gt; frame_invoice_keys()      :23&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;b&gt;── 4C · Parsing ────────────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;i&gt;parsing.py&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br/&gt; parse_payment_value()     :186&lt;br/&gt; parse_main_date()         :82&lt;br/&gt; safe_text() / safe_numeric() :62 / 69&lt;br/&gt; PaymentParseResult [dataclass] :53&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;b&gt;── 4D · Runner / Utils ─────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;i&gt;runner.py&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br/&gt; score_mongo_frame()       :14&lt;br/&gt; &lt;i&gt;utils.py&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br/&gt; flatten_dict()            :53&lt;br/&gt; get_nested() / set_nested() :30 / 39&lt;br/&gt; safe_ratio()              :95 · json_safe() :106&lt;br/&gt; &lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;" parent="40" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="2" y="44" width="274" height="712" as="geometry"/>
