                <mxCell id="50" value="FEATURE ENGINEERING  ·  features/" style="swimlane;startSize=42;fillColor=#FFE6CC;strokeColor=#D79B00;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#1a1a1a;swimlaneLine=1;rounded=4;arcSize=2;align=center;" parent="1" tooltip="FEATURE ENGINEERING — features/  ENTRY: build_risk_main_feature_frame(canonical_df) -&gt; feature_matrix_df  Internal chain:   -&gt; _add_calendar_features()   [DOW/month/quarter cols]   -&gt; _add_frequency_features()  [*_freq cols]   -&gt; _add_entity_history_risk_features() [entity_* cols]   -&gt; _add_additional_customer_history_features() [cust_* cols]   -&gt; add_customer_aggregates()  [merges history_agg_df]   -&gt; add_point_in_time_customer_features() [PIT-safe, no leakage]   -&gt; select_model_features()    [XGBoost input column list]  Output: feature_matrix_df with all engineered + validated columns" vertex="1">
