                <mxCell id="51" value="&lt;div style=&quot;font-family:monospace;font-size:10px;line-height:1.7;padding:4px;color:#1a1a1a;&quot;&gt; &lt;b&gt;── 5A · Engineering ────────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;i&gt;engineering.py&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br/&gt; build_risk_main_feature_frame() :275&lt;br/&gt; _add_calendar_features()  :28&lt;br/&gt; _add_frequency_features() :55&lt;br/&gt; _add_additional_customer_history_features() :67&lt;br/&gt; _add_entity_history_risk_features() :183&lt;br/&gt; _terms_bucket()           :156&lt;br/&gt; _amount_bucket()          :166&lt;br/&gt; _compose_key()            :175&lt;br/&gt; _safe_text_col()          :12 · _safe_num_col() :24&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;b&gt;── 5B · Customer History ───────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;i&gt;customer_aggregates.py&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br/&gt; customer_ids_from_frame() :27&lt;br/&gt; build_customer_history_aggregates() :39&lt;br/&gt; merge_customer_history_aggregates() :80&lt;br/&gt; add_customer_aggregates() :94&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;b&gt;── 5C · Point-in-Time ──────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;i&gt;point_in_time.py&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br/&gt; add_point_in_time_customer_features() :26&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;b&gt;── 5D · Registry / Validation ──&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;i&gt;production_registry.py&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br/&gt; validate_production_columns() :54&lt;br/&gt; select_model_features()   :59&lt;br/&gt; &lt;i&gt;registry.py&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br/&gt; validate_required_columns() :138&lt;br/&gt; SEGMENT_COL [constant]&lt;br/&gt; filter_segment()  segment_filters.py:8&lt;br/&gt; &lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;" parent="50" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="2" y="44" width="274" height="712" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="60" value="SCORING ENGINE  ·  scoring/" style="swimlane;startSize=42;fillColor=#D0E0F0;strokeColor=#3A6EA5;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#1a1a1a;swimlaneLine=1;rounded=4;arcSize=2;align=center;" parent="1" tooltip="SCORING ENGINE — scoring/  LOAD (cached after startup):   load_risk_main_registry() -&gt; risk_main_registry.json   _select_risk_main_entry() -&gt; champion: risk_main_xgb_20260319_094014   load_production_artifacts() -&gt; XGBoost .pkl + sklearn preprocessor .pkl  INFERENCE — score_production_frame(feature_matrix_df):   1. preprocessor.transform()   2. model.predict_proba() -&gt; delay_prob   3. threshold -&gt; risk_band (High/Medium/Low)   4. SHAP top-N features -&gt; top_features list[dict]  OUTPUT: scored_df = feature_matrix_df + risk_score + risk_band + delay_prob + top_features" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1590" y="30" width="280" height="760" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="61" value="&lt;div style=&quot;font-family:monospace;font-size:10px;line-height:1.7;padding:4px;color:#1a1a1a;&quot;&gt; &lt;b&gt;── Model Loading ───────────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;i&gt;model.py&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br/&gt; load_risk_main_registry()  :57&lt;br/&gt; _select_risk_main_entry()  :97&lt;br/&gt; _resolve_threshold_from_registry_entry() :80&lt;br/&gt; load_production_artifacts() :145&lt;br/&gt; describe_active_production_model() :128&lt;br/&gt; get_active_production_model_family() :33&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;b&gt;── Inference ───────────────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; score_production_frame()   :191&lt;br/&gt;   preprocessor.transform()&lt;br/&gt;   xgb.predict_proba()&lt;br/&gt;   → risk_score   [float]&lt;br/&gt;   → risk_band    [High / Med / Low]&lt;br/&gt;   → delay_prob   [float]&lt;br/&gt;   → top_features [list[dict]]&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;b&gt;── Decisioning ─────────────────&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;i&gt;decisioning.py&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br/&gt; build_credit_suggestions() :29&lt;br/&gt; _feature_names()           :17&lt;br/&gt; &lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;" parent="60" vertex="1">
