                <mxCell id="91" value="&lt;div style=&quot;font-family: monospace; line-height: 1.7; padding: 6px; color: rgb(26, 26, 26);&quot;&gt; &lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;DataFrame Flow Legend&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt; ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────&lt;br&gt; &lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;[MongoDB cursor]&lt;/b&gt;       Raw nested docs from Risk.Main&lt;br&gt; &lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;[raw_canonical_df]&lt;/b&gt;     Flat normalized frame · all Risk.Main fields parsed&lt;br&gt; &lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;[feature_matrix_df]&lt;/b&gt;    XGBoost-ready · output of select_model_features()&lt;br&gt; &lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;[scored_df]&lt;/b&gt;            + risk_score  + risk_band  + delay_prob  + top_features&lt;br&gt; &lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;[paged_response]&lt;/b&gt;       JSON {rows, cursor, total, summary} to frontend&lt;br&gt; &lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;[history_agg_df]&lt;/b&gt;       Customer-level aggregate statistics&lt;br&gt; &lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;[customer_frame_df]&lt;/b&gt;    scored_df rows filtered to one customer_id&lt;br&gt; ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────&lt;br&gt; Arrow key:  ──▶  call / data flow     - - ▶  return / response&lt;br&gt; Hover any block for detailed internal call chain.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;" parent="90" vertex="1">
